n hold agro any better with a 1hander than you can with FD. Yes you'll lose a little bit of AC, but you'll be doing alot more damage.<br><br>If you are getting FD in a week or two then I would sell/trade whichever 1hander you can get the most for or maybe both. <p><b>Galadril Adamante<BR>Officer, Order of the White Dragon<BR>Knight of Tunare<BR>Bristlebane Server<BR><a href=mailto:sblue@bright.net>sblue@bright.net</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueqguavus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>EQGuavus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/25/02 3:33:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=286.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Very strange......</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  That you wear Scaled knight guantlets instead of Thunder Etched. I guess normal rules don't apply to some folks in Fusion.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>Oh Tovar, do get over it already. Stop being so sulky just because you were removed from the guild. <p>"Is it always the King who hangs?"- From the works of Kay<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=116313" target="_blank">Guavus' profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueqguavus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>EQGuavus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/25/02 3:38:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=286.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span c